cs.HC, cs.VR, cs.CYBER, cs.RO, cs.MM 

The paper discusses the use of Mixed Reality, specifically Augmented and Virtual Reality, in industrial applications. This topic falls under the Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) and Virtual Reality (cs.VR) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper touches upon cybersecurity concerns (cs.CYBER) and the use of robotics (cs.RO) in industrial settings. Finally, the paper also discusses multimedia (cs.MM) aspects of Mixed Reality.
